---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Pricing — Vestara DST 1031 Education"
  description="Choose between our free 5-day DST email course or the complete $39 Essential Guide — both independent, unbiased, and built for retiring landlords."
>

  <!-- =====================================================================
       HERO
       ===================================================================== -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-20 md:py-28">
    <!-- Layered gradient background — light cream with subtle navy/gold radials -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 10% 80%, oklch(0.65 0.18 70 / 0.07), transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 90% 10%, oklch(0.31 0.10 243 / 0.06), transparent 50%),
        linear-gradient(to bottom, oklch(0.985 0.006 80), oklch(0.965 0.010 78));"
    ></div>

    <!-- Top gold rule -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-48 h-px" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #C9922A, transparent);"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <!-- Eyebrow -->
      <p class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest animate-slide-up mb-5"
         style="color: #C9922A;">
        <span class="block w-8 h-px" style="background:#C9922A;"></span>
        Simple, Transparent Pricing
        <span class="block w-8 h-px" style="background:#C9922A;"></span>
      </p>

      <!-- H1 -->
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight font-display leading-[1.1] animate-slide-up delay-100"
          style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
        Choose Your Path to
        <em class="not-italic" style="color: #C9922A;">DST Clarity</em>
      </h1>

      <!-- Sub-headline -->
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed animate-slide-up delay-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto"
         style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
        Both options are independent, unbiased, and built specifically for retiring landlords — not brokers.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- =====================================================================
       PRICING CARDS
       ===================================================================== -->
  <section class="pb-20 md:pb-28" style="background: oklch(0.965 0.010 78);">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-stretch">

        <!-- ── Card 1: Free ── -->
        <div class="animate-slide-up rounded-2xl border p-8 flex flex-col bg-white"
             style="border-color: oklch(0.92 0.012 76);">

          <!-- Badge -->
          <span class="inline-block self-start px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider rounded-full mb-5"
                style="background: oklch(0.93 0.04 240); color: oklch(0.31 0.10 243);">
            Always Free
          </span>

          <!-- Name + description -->
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight font-display" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
            DST Starter Course
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.65);">
            The essentials of DST 1031 exchanges, delivered in plain English over 5 days.
          </p>

          <!-- Price -->
          <div class="mt-8 flex items-baseline gap-1">
            <span class="text-5xl font-extrabold font-display" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">$0</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Feature list -->
          <ul class="mt-8 space-y-3.5 flex-1">
            {[
              "5-day DST email course",
              "Capital gains tax overview",
              "Plain-English DST explainer",
              "What \"like-kind property\" actually means",
              "Questions to ask your CPA",
            ].map((feature) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.80);">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.2" stroke="currentColor" style="color: oklch(0.31 0.10 243);">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
                </svg>
                <span>{feature}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>

          <!-- CTA -->
          <a
            href="/#guide"
            class="mt-8 block text-center px-6 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-base transition-colors duration-150"
            style="background: oklch(0.93 0.04 240); color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);"
            onmouseover="this.style.background='oklch(0.85 0.07 240)'"
            onmouseout="this.style.background='oklch(0.93 0.04 240)'"
          >
            Get the Free Course
          </a>

          <!-- Trust note -->
          <p class="mt-3 text-center text-xs" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.50);">
            No credit card. No sales calls.
          </p>
        </div>


        <!-- ── Card 2: Essential Guide ($39) — Highlighted ── -->
        <div class="animate-slide-up delay-100 rounded-2xl flex flex-col relative"
             style="background: white; border: 2px solid oklch(0.31 0.10 243); box-shadow: 0 8px 40px oklch(0.31 0.10 243 / 0.14);">

          <!-- Navy top accent bar -->
          <div class="rounded-t-2xl h-1.5 w-full" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, oklch(0.31 0.10 243), oklch(0.25 0.09 243));"></div>

          <div class="p-8 flex flex-col flex-1">
            <!-- Badge -->
            <span class="inline-block self-start px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider rounded-full mb-5"
                  style="background: #C9922A; color: #fff;">
              Most Popular
            </span>

            <!-- Name + description -->
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight font-display" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
              Essential Guide
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.65);">
              The complete DST 1031 playbook for retiring real estate investors — every detail, in order.
            </p>

            <!-- Price -->
            <div class="mt-8 flex items-baseline gap-2">
              <span class="text-5xl font-extrabold font-display" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">$39</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.55);">one-time</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature list -->
            <ul class="mt-8 space-y-3.5 flex-1">
              {[
                "Everything in the Free Course",
                "Full 60-page DST 1031 Guide (PDF)",
                "Capital gains tax deferral worksheet",
                "Accredited investor qualification checklist",
                "Side-by-side tax comparison scenarios",
                "Vetted DST adviser directory (25+ firms)",
                "Lifetime access + future updates",
              ].map((feature, i) => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.80);">
                  <svg
                    class="w-5 h-5 shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                    fill="none"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    stroke-width="2.2"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    style={i === 0 ? "color: #C9922A;" : "color: oklch(0.31 0.10 243);"}
                  >
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
                  </svg>
                  <span class={i === 0 ? "font-semibold" : ""}>{feature}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>

            <!-- CTA -->
            <a
              href="https://api.willo.ai/api/checkout/1e3253f0-f686-4b16-a8ac-40bbafc130cb/price_1TOUIuBlvU0D02EB2R6CyyGQ"
              class="mt-8 block text-center px-6 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-base transition-colors duration-150"
              style="background: oklch(0.31 0.10 243); color: #fff;"
              onmouseover="this.style.background='oklch(0.25 0.09 243)'"
              onmouseout="this.style.background='oklch(0.31 0.10 243)'"
            >
              Get the Essential Guide
            </a>

            <!-- Trust note -->
            <p class="mt-3 text-center text-xs" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.50);">
              One-time payment. No subscription.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>


      <!-- ── Trust Bar ── -->
      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 animate-slide-up delay-200">
        {[
          { icon: "M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z", label: "Independent — no broker commissions" },
          { icon: "M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z", label: "Written for retiring landlords, not finance pros" },
          { icon: "M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 006 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 016 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 016-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0018 18a8.967 8.967 0 00-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25", label: "IRS-compliant educational content" },
          { icon: "M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z", label: "30-day satisfaction guarantee" },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-2 px-4 py-5 rounded-xl"
               style="background: oklch(0.985 0.006 80); border: 1px solid oklch(0.92 0.012 76);">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor" style="color: #C9922A;">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d={item.icon} />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-xs font-medium leading-snug" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.75);">
              {item.label}
            </p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- =====================================================================
       FAQ SECTION
       ===================================================================== -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28" style="background: oklch(0.985 0.006 80);">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

      <!-- Section header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <span class="block w-12 h-0.5 mx-auto mb-6" style="background:#C9922A;"></span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight font-display animate-slide-up"
            style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
          Common Questions
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed animate-slide-up delay-100"
           style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.65);">
          Straight answers — no fine print, no sales pitch.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ items -->
      <div class="space-y-6 animate-slide-up delay-200">

        <!-- Q1 -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border p-8" style="background: white; border-color: oklch(0.92 0.012 76);">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-display" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
            Is Vestara a broker or financial adviser?
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
            No. Vestara is an independent educational resource. We are not a registered broker-dealer,
            investment adviser, or attorney. Our guides help retiring landlords understand DST 1031
            exchanges in plain English — so you can have a more informed conversation with your CPA,
            attorney, or licensed adviser. We never earn commissions on any DST transaction.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q2 -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border p-8" style="background: white; border-color: oklch(0.92 0.012 76);">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-display" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
            Who is the Essential Guide written for?
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
            Retiring landlords with appreciated real estate who want to exit their properties without
            handing a third of their gains to the IRS. You don't need a finance degree — the guide is
            written in plain English, walks through every step in order, and includes worksheets and
            checklists you can bring directly to your professional advisers. If you own one or more
            rental properties and are within 10 years of retirement, it was written specifically for you.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q3 -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border p-8" style="background: white; border-color: oklch(0.92 0.012 76);">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-display" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
            When will I receive the guide?
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
            Immediately after purchase — delivered as a PDF to the inbox you provide at checkout.
            There's no waiting, no shipping, and no account to create. Your download link is
            permanent and yours to keep. If you ever lose access or need a re-send, email us at
            <a href="mailto:hello@vestara.com" class="font-medium underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors duration-150"
               style="color: oklch(0.31 0.10 243);">hello@vestara.com</a>
            and we'll get it to you within one business day.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- =====================================================================
       BOTTOM CTA
       ===================================================================== -->
  <section id="cta" class="py-20 md:py-28 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Navy gradient background -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 50%, oklch(0.65 0.18 70 / 0.10), transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, oklch(0.45 0.10 240 / 0.15), transparent 50%),
        linear-gradient(145deg, oklch(0.20 0.020 243) 0%, oklch(0.25 0.09 243) 60%, oklch(0.31 0.10 243) 100%);"
    ></div>

    <!-- Gold top rule -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #C9922A, transparent);"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <span class="block w-12 h-0.5 mx-auto mb-6" style="background:#C9922A;"></span>

      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight font-display animate-slide-up"
          style="color: oklch(0.985 0.006 80);">
        Still on the fence? Start free.<br/>
        <em class="not-italic" style="color: #C9922A;">Upgrade when you're ready.</em>
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed animate-slide-up delay-100"
         style="color: oklch(0.85 0.012 76 / 0.80);">
        The free 5-day course is a genuine starting point — not a teaser. Most readers finish it
        knowing more than they ever expected. The Essential Guide simply goes deeper.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 animate-slide-up delay-200">
        <a
          href="/#guide"
          class="inline-block px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-base transition-colors duration-150"
          style="background:#C9922A; color:#fff;"
          onmouseover="this.style.background='oklch(0.55 0.17 68)'"
          onmouseout="this.style.background='#C9922A'"
        >
          Get the Free Course
        </a>
        <a
          href="STRIPE_PLACEHOLDER_URL"
          class="inline-block px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-base border transition-colors duration-150"
          style="border-color: oklch(0.85 0.012 76 / 0.30); color: oklch(0.985 0.006 80);"
          onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='oklch(0.85 0.012 76 / 0.60)'"
          onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='oklch(0.85 0.012 76 / 0.30)'"
        >
          Get the Essential Guide — $39
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-5 text-sm animate-slide-up delay-300" style="color: oklch(0.85 0.012 76 / 0.45);">
        No commissions, ever. Independent educational resource.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
